holocaust
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:(controversially) applied in NZ contexts, esp. to the Parihaka operation against Taranaki Maori
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: phrase originally used in Waitangi Tribunal Taranaki report; later approved & adopted by Tariana Turia
